- MORE places categories
- Points of interest
- Car Traffic info
- Satellite mode for map
- Subway lines on map
- A map of Lisbon's underground in portrait modes;
- A route planner between stations with two selection methods (diagram selection or name selection);
- Showing duration and list of stations in a route;
- A map route to station from your position (walking or driving);
- Show diagram's selected station on map;
- Detailed information per Station;
- Support for multiple screen sizes and resolutions;
- In English, Portuguese, Portuguese Brazilian, German, Spanish, French, Italian, Swedish, Russian and Dutch
